{"tid":1236130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐警隊 反暴力 民間聲援大會","createTime":"2019-06-17T10:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:44:15.000Z","uid":84633,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab260594f3942897408a02dc45a89de3bbd63cb","tid":1236130,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"唔係玩膠，何妖真係搞呢個大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n撐警隊 反暴力，媽，我好亂啊<br />\n//何君堯 (Junius Ho Kwan Yiu) 和何君堯在一起。<br />\n<br />\n【撐警隊 反暴力 民間聲援大會】<br />\n《大會主題》<br />\n為警隊打氣、為香港打氣<br />\n日期：6月30日 星期日<br />\n時間：下午3-6點<br />\n地點：金鐘添馬公園<br />\n<br />\n邀請各界市民出席集會，為警隊打氣。<br />\n《大會呼籲》<br />\n歡迎不同團體及市民出席，是次活動為民間自發活動，香港政研會只為籌辦及執行單位，大會主辦及參與者皆為市民個人，不分彼此。<br />\n本活動不接受任何捐款捐獻，也不會安排任何物資派發，我們只需要您的氣場，為香港未來打氣。<br />\n#撐警隊反暴力<br />\n#支持香港警察<br />\n#有效執法<br />\n#何君堯//"},{"pid":"17dbbb4ead889a04f129067038c89b6ddca9cd91","tid":1236130,"uid":214672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:58:29.000Z","msg":"歡迎不同團體<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa51985e8d80dc763eb87c571515eebd8d2082f","tid":1236130,"uid":148332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:59:13.000Z","msg":"休班警都唔會去參加啦,咁大陣柒味,唔驚比人影到笑成世咩"},{"pid":"e713f43bfd1218c530e0719eb27969daab182efa","tid":1236130,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"30號要人<br />\n發夢時見到撐警聯盟會一車車蝗蟲落嚟暴力打市民<br />\n同當年佔中時一樣"},{"pid":"3633f624bfbbb65992b7dae50683aa66e16fa32e","tid":1236130,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e713f43bfd1218c530e0719eb27969daab182efa","tid":1236130,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T10:59:23.000Z","msg":"30號要人<br />\n發夢時見到撐警聯盟會一車車蝗蟲落嚟暴力打市民<br />\n同當年佔中時一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"果日有特別事?<br />\n無既咪畀個場佢地囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bc4b865794eb8c690aedfea5d18f58255d179b","tid":1236130,"uid":82974,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"全程得黑警暴力，點樣撐黑警又反暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c13cd00f1ba011080f60740b7cadd769bc7ced","tid":1236130,"uid":84044,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:13:40.000Z","msg":"究竟佢想撐警隊定反暴力架？"},{"pid":"b479388cf475ab17fb0a5dc41b87f28ce89751a3","tid":1236130,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"撐警隊定反暴力呀?<br />\n打佢定打佢老母呀?!"},{"pid":"2a75ac6903fde70326d7b33e13ef158973b796b4","tid":1236130,"uid":92734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:42:35.000Z","msg":"呢鋪要僧侶團出動"},{"pid":"e838bee0d763258822049665af48acac1b4549a6","tid":1236130,"uid":139916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"有冇人到時帶兩隻紙紮人參加"}]}